{"type":null,"faqId":47253,"title":"如何为联系人设置头像？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:#333333;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">存储在 SIM 卡中的联系人不支持设置头像，仅支持为存储在手机中的联系人设置头像。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">进入联系人详情界面，选择“修改”，点击联系人头像位置。选择一种图片来源，根据屏幕提示调整图片并保存设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">也可以通过“图库”或“文件管理”中的图片设置联系人头像：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">打开要设置为联系人头像的图片，打开选项菜单，在更多选项中点击“设置为 &gt; 联系人照片”，选择手机中存储的联系人，根据屏幕提示调整图片并保存设置。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2820","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219134000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":39,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"联系人,头像","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}